<p><img width="141" height="125" class="wp-image-3795 aligncenter size-full" alt="" src="https://i0.wp.com/burkebasicschool.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/update.png?resize=141%2C125&amp;ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1"></p>
<p>Parents, for those picking up packets, they can <strong>stay with you</strong>.  Packets do not need to be returned to the school in efforts to ensure health and safety of everyone.</p>
<p>School will remain closed through the end of the school year per announcment by the Office of the Govenor. <a href="https://azgovernor.gov/governor/news/2020/03/governor-ducey-superintendent-hoffman-announce-extension-school-closures"> See link here.</a></p>
<p>=====================================</p>
<p>Padres, para aquellos que recogen paquetes, pueden <strong>quedarse con ustedes</strong>. No es necesario devolver los paquetes a la escuela en un esfuerzo por garantizar la salud y la seguridad de todos.  La escuela permanecerá cerrada hasta el final del año escolar por anuncio de la Oficina del Gobernador.<a href="https://azgovernor.gov/governor/news/2020/03/governor-ducey-superintendent-hoffman-announce-extension-school-closures"> Ver enlace aquí</a></p>
